modName: Wuuthrad Fix - Rise of the Legend - Ysgramor
summary: This makes it so newermind43's custom Wuuthrad doesn't replace the vanilla one.
descriptionHtml:
This makes it so newermind43's custom Wuuthrad doesn't replace the vanilla one. This is just a temporary quick fix until the actual issue is fixed. If newermind43 wants me to take this down, or if newermind43 fixes this in his next update, I'll take down this mod.

This mod does not take up a plugin space.

The reason his fix didn't work for Wuuthrad in his mod is that there are two Wuuthrads in game, and he accidentally only fixed the one that is held by Ysgramor.

This requires Rise of the Legend - Ysgramor to use. It will literally do nothing if it is not installed. You can find it here:
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53581/?

Recommended mods:
aMidianBorn Book of Silence:
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24909/?

Bethesda - For making the Wuuthrad model.
